Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.18,0:20:12.27,Insert,,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally that time we've been waiting for. Are U Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.94,0:20:19.23,Insert,,0000,0000,0000,,The Cook Girl's heart throbs. Make it well, and make some smiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.23,0:20:23.86,Insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet announcing, "I'll eat anything."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.86,0:20:26.74,Insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't slack off (*_*) Let's make!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.74,0:20:30.08,Insert,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll cook up our own special.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.83,0:20:36.58,Insert,,0000,0000,0000,,No exceptions at all?! All girls love sweets!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.92,0:20:42.01,Insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's pretend to forget counting calories, just for one day!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.38,0:20:48.68,Insert,,0000,0000,0000,,If we slip up a bit, it's all good. Our failures are still a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.68,0:20:54.69,Insert,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the thought that counts, right? The burnt parts show our love.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.94,0:21:03.19,Insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady munching Cake!
