Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.30,0:00:05.61,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.61,0:00:06.94,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.66,0:00:11.14,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,It's gotten cold all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.14,0:00:13.28,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's almost the end of October, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.90,0:00:15.95,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Halloween.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.12,0:00:17.12,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.12,0:00:21.76,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, Halloween decorations are starting to show up everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.76,0:00:23.02,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.02,0:00:26.71,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like it's become a tradition in Japan now, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.09,0:00:28.79,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,No kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.33,0:00:30.79,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.79,0:00:33.55,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Er... huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.42,0:00:36.55,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.04,0:00:40.59,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,You can't have Halloween without ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.96,0:00:44.64,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.41,0:00:47.26,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.26,0:00:50.42,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, Halloween ghosts aren't real ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.42,0:00:54.20,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a little uncomfortable with scary stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.62,0:00:56.28,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.59,0:00:59.08,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.65,0:01:03.03,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi, I'll bet there are things you're uncomfortable with, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.03,0:01:05.08,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can't think of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.89,0:01:07.33,A Channel 1,Kitou-sensei,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.14,0:01:10.67,A Channel 1,Kitou-sensei,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Put some spirit in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.32,0:01:12.71,A Channel 1,Student 1,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.71,0:01:14.76,A Channel 1,Kitou-sensei,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.30,0:01:15.34,A Channel 2,Student 2,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}Good morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.26,0:01:18.05,A Channel 1,Kitou-sensei,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.56,0:01:20.26,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you weren't uncomfortable with anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.64,0:01:25.19,A Channel 1,Kitou-sensei,0000,0000,0000,,Let's give it 110% today!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.83,0:01:29.08,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I'm uncomfortable with that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.08,0:01:30.94,A Channel 1,Kitou-sensei,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.68,0:03:09.71,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Nagi-chan, Yuuko-chan! Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.12,0:03:11.57,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.12,0:03:11.57,A Channel 2,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}Morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.57,0:03:15.42,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You two seem worn out. What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.87,0:03:17.58,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,First thing in the morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.58,0:03:19.58,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,hot-blooded.{Senna: I'd go with the noun form, "hot-bloodedness" here, as the adjective doesn't go well with the lack of a subject (for Run, anyway). That and it's not Nagi nor Yuuko who are hot-blooded XD}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.58,0:03:20.93,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.45,0:03:24.10,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone has things they're uncomfortable with.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.62,0:03:25.63,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.63,0:03:26.42,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.36,0:03:29.14,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.78,0:03:31.81,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?{Senna: I'd suggest going with something along the lines of "What's wrong?" or "What's the matter?" here, as "What is it?" can be misinterpreted in a way such that it appears that Yuuko is also asking what the object on Nagi's desk is.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.49,0:03:34.61,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,There's a strange doll on my desk...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:37.59,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh! It's so creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.59,0:03:38.19,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:41.44,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, maybe it has to do with Halloween?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.44,0:03:43.72,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,You know, "Trick-or-Treat"!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.72,0:03:46.26,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,A trick? Is someone harassing me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.26,0:03:48.87,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds likely, that's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:50.99,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Should you throw it away?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.99,0:03:53.50,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,But I might get cursed if I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:56.31,A Channel 2,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,You're right! It'd be terrible if you were cursed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.31,0:03:57.41,A Channel 2,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:57.41,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What do I do? I can't admit that I made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.73,0:04:01.62,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,What? You made that doll, Run?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.62,0:04:03.84,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm so sorry I said those mean things!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:05.51,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.00,0:04:10.34,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,You said you liked them, so I did my best to make one,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.34,0:04:13.09,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,but animals are hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.09,0:04:14.52,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't look like one, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.79,0:04:16.88,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, you did great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.88,0:04:18.08,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.08,0:04:19.23,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Especially these...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.17,0:04:21.69,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,ear-like things...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.73,0:04:23.78,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,no, horns?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:28.78,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,I like the glaring{\fscx200}-{\r} I mean, soulfully gazing eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.24,0:04:34.29,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Right, the mouth! The way it's gaping open is really distinctive!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.68,0:04:37.56,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right! It looks exactly like one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:41.88,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Actually... this thing I'm supposed to like...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:44.06,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}what exactly is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:44.06,A Channel 2,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\i1}What could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.06,0:04:45.94,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,Does it look like one?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.94,0:04:47.39,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.94,0:04:47.39,A Channel 2,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.94,0:04:50.39,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,A Halloween party?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.98,0:04:52.31,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,How did that come up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.58,0:04:55.62,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Well, after an incident this morning, we got on the topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.62,0:04:58.62,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,I've been interested in Halloween for a while now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.62,0:05:02.35,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, tomorrow's Saturday. Let's all make some sweets and eat them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.35,0:05:03.99,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.56,0:05:06.34,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of sweets should we make?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.34,0:05:09.25,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Cookies or something? Or maybe cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.25,0:05:10.89,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.93,0:05:14.50,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi-chan, you don't like making sweets?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.72,0:05:17.41,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Cooking involves all those precise measurements.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.41,0:05:19.41,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,It's not really my thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.99,0:05:22.89,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Also, well, I'm on a diet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.89,0:05:24.85,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.85,0:05:28.89,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'll count the calories carefully, just for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.89,0:05:30.31,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Would you really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.31,0:05:31.66,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.66,0:05:33.55,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if I'm just eating them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.55,0:05:34.23,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,That's more like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.79,0:05:35.94,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Tooru?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.78,0:05:39.82,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll probably be a bit late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.82,0:05:41.28,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.28,0:05:43.95,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,When you're finished, I'll go to your house to eat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.95,0:05:45.11,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,All right then!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.18,0:05:49.09,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll go with Tooru.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.09,0:05:49.95,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.38,0:05:53.65,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, do you want to help me cook, Yuuko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.65,0:05:57.23,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,No problem. Is there anything I should bring?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.23,0:06:00.30,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm. My mom likes to cook sweets,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.30,0:06:02.44,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,so we should have everything we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:04.84,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I'm looking forward to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.02,0:06:07.50,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's do our best tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.50,0:06:08.69,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.41,0:06:25.42,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Run, what are you drawing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.36,0:06:32.56,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,This! It's word chain pictionary for the exchange diary I'm doing with Tooru!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.23,0:06:37.32,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,What does it look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.67,0:06:41.42,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A repeat of that doll incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.54,0:06:51.71,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For starters, is it an animal?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.71,0:06:54.34,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, it sort of resembles a bug...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.34,0:06:56.72,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,Is it too tricky?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.50,0:06:59.84,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,Then here's a hint:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.84,0:07:01.27,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,people often eat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.00,0:07:04.96,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wha... it's edible?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.96,0:07:07.51,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,That was a huge hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.51,0:07:09.28,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,It's a zebra, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:11.49,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,Bullseye, Tooru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:13.28,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Z{\fscx200}-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.98,0:07:15.49,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Zebra?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:17.41,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,Smart as always, Tooru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.41,0:07:19.96,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Th-That's a zebra?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.96,0:07:22.07,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Am I just thick?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.16,0:07:24.74,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi, you're overthinking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.04,0:07:34.97,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy she gave it to me, but it's kind of scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.33,0:07:37.66,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi, you're not leaving yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.66,0:07:39.43,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,No, I was about to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.15,0:07:44.29,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, want to meet up before we go to Run-chan's tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.29,0:07:46.92,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... yeah, that'd be more convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.92,0:07:48.92,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about the North entrance to the station?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.92,0:07:50.96,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,It's near the entrance to the shopping district.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.96,0:07:51.40,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.05,0:07:57.28,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,T-Tooru! Th-That thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:00.29,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:01.87,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.09,0:08:03.97,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, I figured as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.97,0:08:05.00,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,Then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.46,0:08:10.34,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,What's that a doll of?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.75,0:08:16.71,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You can't tell, Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.67,0:08:22.13,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For some reason, this really bugs me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.58,0:08:26.69,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, she gave me something similar...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.25,0:08:28.52,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,It's big!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.66,0:08:33.70,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,No fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.25,0:08:39.23,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,Please, if you would be so kind, allow me to have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.23,0:08:42.75,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why, I couldn't possibly. It belongs to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.26,0:08:45.65,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that{\fscx200}-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.43,0:08:46.23,A Channel 2,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}Can't do it, can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.65,0:08:47.31,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,No fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.31,0:08:49.18,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Why, it's perfectly fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.18,0:08:50.48,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,We're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.29,0:08:53.22,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,Let's head home!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.22,0:08:55.45,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,I need to get ready, so wait up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.45,0:08:57.76,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Make it quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.57,0:09:01.86,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.86,0:09:02.43,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.98,0:09:05.38,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,What's your favorite animal?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.08,0:09:08.94,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're going to use it for word chain pictionary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:10.44,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.69,0:09:12.34,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,I was just curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.91,0:09:14.45,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.02,0:09:16.88,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Let me think.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.88,0:09:19.36,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,I like small animals. They're cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.00,0:09:21.30,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Like squirrels!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.30,0:09:23.37,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, squirrels are cute, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.03,0:09:26.46,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,On that note, this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.87,0:09:29.03,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't say what it was, now did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.03,0:09:30.42,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.98,0:09:32.66,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,We're ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.68,0:09:31.89,A Channel 2,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.89,0:09:33.42,A Channel 2,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes I do! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.83,0:09:35.48,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Come on now, tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.48,0:09:37.41,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,Squirrels are cute, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.41,0:09:38.89,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tooru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.89,0:09:40.33,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,Small animals...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.33,0:09:42.33,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.62,0:09:41.57,A Channel 2,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}Wonder what they're talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.57,0:09:43.18,A Channel 2,Run,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}Who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.90,0:09:46.52,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:04.54,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. Still scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.21,0:10:21.13,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.40,0:10:23.76,A Channel 1,Little Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Trick-or-Treat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:25.31,A Channel 1,Witch,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.31,0:10:26.02,A Channel 1,Little Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.60,0:10:29.34,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Looks like all the stores are decked out in Halloween colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.17,0:10:30.92,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.92,0:10:33.78,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}we were supposed to meet around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.39,0:10:36.79,A Channel 1,Child 1,0000,0000,0000,,I said, "Trick-or-Treat!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.71,0:10:39.46,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.10,0:10:40.88,A Channel 2,Child 2,0000,0000,0000,,Candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.59,0:10:41.59,A Channel 1,Child 1,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hand it over!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.76,0:10:46.74,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,I kept saying I didn't work here, but the little brats...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.23,0:10:49.65,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not even carrying any candy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.65,0:10:50.12,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.33,0:10:56.52,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru, are those supposed to be your casual clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.72,0:11:01.13,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.77,0:11:05.45,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Do we usually pass through this shopping district on the way to Run's?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.45,0:11:06.35,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,Never been here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.35,0:11:07.42,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.42,0:11:11.14,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,If I recall, we went a different way the last time we went to Run's.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.71,0:11:15.03,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,Precisely. This is a slight detour.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.68,0:11:16.39,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,You know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.50,0:11:21.10,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan said she's making sweets, so we need replacement sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.44,0:11:23.66,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so we're here to buy those.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.66,0:11:25.71,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, so it's a given she'll mess up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.67,0:11:28.01,A Channel 1,Shopkeeper 1,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Tooru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.73,0:11:30.83,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.83,0:11:32.07,A Channel 1,Shopkeeper 1,0000,0000,0000,,You're looking well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.53,0:11:34.80,A Channel 1,Shopkeeper 1,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.80,0:11:36.17,A Channel 1,Shopkeeper 1,0000,0000,0000,,Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.63,0:11:40.54,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:44.65,A Channel 1,Shopkeeper 2,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.65,0:11:45.18,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.84,0:11:48.18,A Channel 1,Shopkeeper 2,0000,0000,0000,,Here, have it! It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.74,0:11:50.19,A Channel 1,Shopkeeper 2,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.19,0:11:51.34,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.97,0:11:53.45,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.45,0:11:57.68,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tooru mentioned during the festival that people in the shopping district give her stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:11:59.84,A Channel 1,Elderly 1,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru-chan! Here, take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.84,0:12:01.38,A Channel 1,Elderly 2,0000,0000,0000,,My, you've come to visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.38,0:12:03.28,A Channel 1,Elderly 3,0000,0000,0000,,Here, use this, Tooru.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.93,0:12:06.37,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In fact, she's not paying for anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.01,0:12:10.11,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,What's this all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.52,0:12:13.22,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,We still have time, so we're stopping by this bookstore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.22,0:12:14.05,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.54,0:12:18.29,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, that's perfect. There's a book I want, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.31,0:12:30.88,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tooru, isn't this{\fscx200}-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.91,0:12:45.87,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.43,0:13:33.75,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,In this manga...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.75,0:13:34.49,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.49,0:13:37.20,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,This Yoshinoko looks like Yuuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.20,0:13:39.45,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, isn't that an ero-manga?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.67,0:13:45.25,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you're right. She totally looks the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.25,0:13:47.32,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,Just look at this. It's a short story collection,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.32,0:13:50.97,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,but all the heroines have the same face.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.01,0:14:02.97,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,If we showed the author a photo of Yuuko,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.97,0:14:04.34,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,he'd probably pay good money for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.91,0:14:06.48,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's buy this book.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.12,0:14:08.94,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's get started!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.23,0:14:11.35,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-chan, do you want an apron?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.35,0:14:12.36,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.39,0:14:16.73,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Your mom must be really into making sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.73,0:14:19.32,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, look at all the cute cookie-cutters!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.76,0:14:23.18,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are we allowed to use all the stuff here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.18,0:14:26.12,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. She said to use whatever we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.12,0:14:28.78,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.44,0:14:31.01,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are we making them with?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.14,0:14:33.10,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, hang on a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.82,0:14:34.88,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.57,0:14:38.14,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,This!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.83,0:14:40.07,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,Hotcakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.72,0:14:42.51,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.58,0:14:45.45,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,For Halloween?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.45,0:14:48.76,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. I felt like hotcakes today!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.76,0:14:50.56,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.03,0:14:57.85,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah! The other day, I cracked an egg with one hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.85,0:14:58.66,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.66,0:14:59.32,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,Watch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.62,0:15:32.91,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,The other day, I cracked an egg with one hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.72,0:15:38.99,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Run, let's just move on...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.67,0:15:42.03,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that does it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.03,0:15:43.57,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. This should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.89,0:15:46.64,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put it on the griddle, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.64,0:15:47.34,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.65,0:15:52.01,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.39,0:16:07.77,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Thank good...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.77,0:16:08.89,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,ness!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.59,0:16:15.89,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.55,0:16:27.17,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I'm sorry! I'll redo it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.17,0:16:29.62,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's okay! Don't rush!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.91,0:16:33.83,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,It was my clumsy mistake, so why did Yuuko-chan have to suffer?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.28,0:16:36.75,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on, don't worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.46,0:16:38.60,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.60,0:16:40.88,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,I should suffer instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.88,0:16:41.47,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.90,0:16:43.56,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,Yah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.06,0:16:45.64,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Whaaaaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.62,0:16:48.69,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.74,0:16:50.93,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,Take a bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.41,0:16:52.38,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.76,0:16:59.81,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.81,0:17:00.08,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.51,0:17:03.63,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,Your figure's so nice, Yuuko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.63,0:17:05.39,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.39,0:17:07.16,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because of your pets?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.62,0:17:08.22,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.77,0:17:12.30,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,What was it again? Uh, sounded like an office supply...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:12.91,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.52,0:17:14.82,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,Tapeworms!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.82,0:17:15.96,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,That again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.96,0:17:17.94,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,You use the power of the tapeworms!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.94,0:17:20.61,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, they're not pets, and I don't have any!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.08,0:17:35.45,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Wearing this, in someone else's house...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.21,0:17:40.25,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave your change of clothes in the living room, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.43,0:17:44.50,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,I should have asked her to bring it when we got in the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.96,0:17:48.02,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,Dynamite!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.94,0:17:50.00,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You were here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.72,0:17:52.60,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,Such immodesty, and in someone else's house!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.60,0:17:55.26,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't recall raising such an indecent daughter as you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.70,0:17:57.05,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:17:58.86,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.86,0:18:00.94,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you speak to me like that, father?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.94,0:18:04.56,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What? Nagi, what's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.95,0:18:08.79,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,We've been practicing for your sake, so listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.79,0:18:09.72,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Practicing what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.76,0:18:14.23,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,What is that manga?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.65,0:18:18.16,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,We found a sexy manga starring your lookalike.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.16,0:18:21.12,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,What? No! A perverted manga?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.68,0:18:23.84,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Here, take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.84,0:18:27.86,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,No, stop it! I hate perverted stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.20,0:18:30.30,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.16,0:18:34.66,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.23,0:18:39.73,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,So she says, but she'll read the whole thing at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.28,0:18:37.91,A Channel 2,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.73,0:18:41.64,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-chan, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.23,0:18:42.80,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,Hey{\fscx200}-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.75,0:18:46.42,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Tooru?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.42,0:18:48.09,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,Not for you, Run-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.09,0:18:50.57,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm glad you like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.57,0:18:51.55,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.61,0:18:55.26,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Look at all the snacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.83,0:18:59.08,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru got these all for free at the shopping district.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.08,0:19:01.06,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing, Tooru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.06,0:19:02.24,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,But what a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.72,0:19:06.61,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,I was hoping we could all eat hotcakes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.45,0:19:10.33,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Run-chan's hotcakes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.71,0:19:12.09,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,but we screwed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.86,0:19:13.83,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sweat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.24,0:19:18.92,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. But I still wish we could have had hotcakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.92,0:19:20.58,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Just make them next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.95,0:19:23.15,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.85,0:19:26.13,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,Well, shall we get started?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.46,0:19:27.95,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's have a toast!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.31,0:19:32.69,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's Halloween, should we toast the ghosts?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.83,0:19:35.66,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should. Or how about {\i1}no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.54,0:19:38.44,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.81,0:19:39.56,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.04,0:19:43.44,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make some now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.70,0:19:45.35,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.17,0:19:50.05,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,Make it again? But we're out of hotcake mix.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.05,0:19:51.32,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.02,0:19:54.99,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.10,0:19:57.33,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,We can make them with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.68,0:20:02.95,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.95,0:20:03.70,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.72,0:20:09.84,A Channel 1 IN,Run,0000,0000,0000,,Eggs!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.84,0:20:10.93,A Channel 1 IN,Run,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.44,0:20:19.67,A Channel 1 IN,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,We're grilling them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.92,0:20:41.35,A Channel 1 IN,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,And it's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.29,0:20:43.95,A Channel 1 IN,Run,0000,0000,0000,,It's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.95,0:20:45.47,A Channel 1 IN,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Mmm, looks good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.47,0:20:47.29,A Channel 1 IN,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,We made it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.29,0:20:48.70,A Channel 1 IN,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.70,0:20:49.22,A Channel 1 IN,Run,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.03,0:20:51.63,A Channel 1 IN,All,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.31,0:20:53.96,A Channel 1 IN,Run,0000,0000,0000,,It looks good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.51,0:21:00.56,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,It is good!{Senna: Suggest either emphasizing the "is", or simply contracting "It is" to "It's"...}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.81,0:21:02.19,A Channel 1 IN,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Mm, delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.90,0:21:08.07,A Channel 1 IN,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.42,0:21:09.73,A Channel 1 IN,Run,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru, you've got a piece on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.35,0:21:15.20,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Yuuko. Say "ahh".
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.20,0:21:16.54,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.12,0:21:26.92,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'm stuffed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.27,0:21:29.53,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi, what about your diet?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.53,0:21:32.90,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Wha{\fscx200}-{\r} I thought you were counting the calories!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.90,0:21:36.22,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I made the recipe less sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.22,0:21:38.70,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, don't scare me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.28,0:21:40.85,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.55,0:21:43.37,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,We'll clean up together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.37,0:21:44.06,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.06,0:21:45.61,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, your outfit, Tooru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.98,0:21:48.00,A Channel 1,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like cosplay. It's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.01,0:21:49.78,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.28,0:21:53.15,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to those clothes, the kids were all over her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.44,0:21:55.90,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,Really? How nice, Tooru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.90,0:21:59.33,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, they were tugging at her clothes and crying at her...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.33,0:22:02.74,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you should have handed out candy, like last year?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.79,0:22:04.61,A Channel 1,Nagi + Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.66,0:22:08.51,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru likes kids, so last year{\fscx200}-
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.51,0:22:10.47,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to tell them that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.47,0:22:12.09,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Tooru?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.32,0:22:18.56,A Channel 1,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru, totally unexpected!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.32,0:22:18.56,A Channel 2,Yuuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}Tooru, totally unexpected!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.56,0:22:19.39,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,You've got it wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.39,0:22:21.11,A Channel 1,Run,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru loves kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.11,0:22:22.93,A Channel 1,Tooru,0000,0000,0000,,You've got it wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.73,0:23:58.72,A Channel 1,Miporin,0000,0000,0000,,What's this title supposed to be? A drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.72,0:24:01.35,A Channel 1,Yutaka,0000,0000,0000,,Playing the fool when you know the answer, isn't it sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.35,0:24:03.46,A Channel 1,Miporin,0000,0000,0000,,That was 'cause the audience expects it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.46,0:24:04.54,A Channel 1,Miporin + Yutaka,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on A-Channel!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.54,0:24:05.52,A Channel 1,Miporin + Yutaka,0000,0000,0000,,"Carbonation"!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.52,0:24:07.80,A Channel 1,Yutaka,0000,0000,0000,,Requesting Yutaka and Toorun for next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.80,0:24:08.51,A Channel 1,Miporin,0000,0000,0000,,Denied.
